# ============================================================
# README.md
# ============================================================

make-file "README.md" with ---
# MintCore v1.0

Centralized virtual currency engine — FastAPI + SQLAlchemy + Typer CLI.

## Quickstart

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn main:app --reload
# API docs: http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs
```

## CLI usage

```bash
python cli.py create-currency GLD Gold G --supply-cap 1000000
python cli.py mint player1 500 GLD
python cli.py transfer player1 player2 100 GLD
python cli.py tax 5 GLD
python cli.py loan player1 200 GLD
python cli.py apply-interest
python cli.py richlist GLD
python cli.py stats
python cli.py ledger
python cli.py ledger player1
```

## Tests

```bash
pytest tests/
```

## Layout

```
mintcore/
├── main.py              # app entrypoint + startup
├── config.py            # ADMIN_KEY, DEBT_CAP, etc.
├── database.py          # engine, SessionLocal, get_db
├── models.py            # SQLAlchemy ORM
├── schemas.py           # Pydantic schemas
├── helpers.py           # get_or_create_wallet, log_tx
├── cli.py               # Typer + Rich admin CLI
├── routers/
│   ├── users.py         # /users
│   ├── transactions.py  # /transactions/transfer, /repay, /ledger
│   ├── admin.py         # /admin/* (currency, mint, burn, tax, loan, rates)
│   ├── rates.py         # /rate/{base}/{target}
│   └── analytics.py     # /analytics/supply, velocity, richlist, debt, stats
└── tests/
    └── test_engine.py
```
